Class TabBarActivity

java.lang.Object

                          de.sarahw.ma.phone.TabBarActivity
All Implemented Interfaces:
ComponentCallbacks, KeyEvent.Callback, LayoutInflater.Factory, View.OnCreateContextMenuListener, Window.Callback
public class TabBarActivity
extends TabActivity

The TabBarActivity class holding the application activities. Initializes the necessary members for a bluetooth connection.

Bluetooth code adapted from https://github.com/luugiathuy/Remote-Bluetooth-Android (RemoteBluetooth.java)

Modified 2011-09-18

Author:
Luu Gia Thuy (RemoteBluetooth.java), Sarah Will (RemoteBluetooth.java modifications, additional code)
